## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not encompass all possible strategies for crime reduction. The findings are limited to the perspectives and data presented in the selected sources. Additionally, the effectiveness of the strategies discussed may vary based on local contexts and specific societal dynamics. Further research and localized studies are recommended to tailor these strategies to specific communities.